-<http://data.bgs.ac.uk/id/Lexicon/NamedRockUnit/WHOC> <http://data.bgs.ac.uk/ref/Lexicon/hasLateralEquivalent> <http://data.bgs.ac.uk/id/Lexicon/NamedRockUnit/S343> .
