-<http://data.bgs.ac.uk/id/Lexicon/NamedRockUnit/WINC> <http://data.bgs.ac.uk/ref/Lexicon/hasLateralEquivalent> <http://data.bgs.ac.uk/id/Lexicon/NamedRockUnit/S904> .
-<http://data.bgs.ac.uk/id/Lexicon/NamedRockUnit/WMC> <http://data.bgs.ac.uk/ref/Lexicon/hasLateralEquivalent> <http://data.bgs.ac.uk/id/Lexicon/NamedRockUnit/S604> .
